high_descs: Turn right and go toward the fridge, then turn left and go to the counter straight ahead.
Pick up the pot on the counter.
Turn around and go straight, then turn left at the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot inside and chill it, then take it out.
Go to your left, to the counter adjacent to the fridge.
Open the cabinet beneath the counter, place the pot inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the fridge, then hang a left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the large metal pot off of the counter.
Walk back over to the fridge.
Put the metal pot in the fridge for a couple seconds to get cold, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, then turn right again to face the counter.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door in front of you and put the chilled metal pot inside, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pot in the cabinet.

high_descs: go the counter by the fridge
get the pan from the counter
take the pan to the fridge
put inside to chill then remove
take the pan to the cabinet to the left of the fridge
put the pan in the bottom cabinet
anns.task_desc: chill the pan in the fridge before putting it in the cabinet
